<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Bon d'examen laboratoire</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0f4c81;
            --primary-light: #edf5fc;
            --border: #cfd8e3;
            --text: #1f2937;
            --muted: #6b7280;
            --light: #f8fafc;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @page {
            size: A5 portrait;
            margin: 6mm;
        }

        body {
            font-family: DejaVu Sans, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--text);
            margin: 0;
            background: #fff;
            line-height: 1.35;
        }

        .page {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .document {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 8px 10px 7px;
        }

        .header-top {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
        }

        .header-left,
        .header-center,
        .header-right {
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .header-left {
            width: 18%;
        }

        .header-center {
            width: 54%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 6px;
        }

        .header-right {
            width: 28%;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 52px;
            max-height: 52px;
        }

        .qr {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .clinic-name {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .clinic-meta {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 2px 0 2px;
            letter-spacing: .2px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .ref-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 4px 6px;
            background: var(--light);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .ref-box:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .ref-box .label {
            font-size: 7px;
            color: var(--muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1px;
        }

        .ref-box .value {
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 8px 10px 10px;
        }

        .badge-destination {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 1px solid #d7e8f7;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .section-grid {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            border-spacing: 0;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .section-col {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .section-col:first-child {
            padding-right: 4px;
        }

        .section-col:last-child {
            padding-left: 4px;
        }

        .card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 7px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fff;
            min-height: 98px;
        }

        .card-header {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 5px 7px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 6px 7px;
        }

        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .info-table td {
            padding: 2px 0;
            vertical-align: top;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 8.5px;
        }

        .info-table td.label {
            width: 42%;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            padding-right: 4px;
        }

        .info-table td.value {
            width: 58%;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .exam-section-title {
            margin: 8px 0 5px;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
            padding-left: 6px;
        }

        .exam-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .exam-table th,
        .exam-table td {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 5px 5px;
            text-align: left;
            vertical-align: top;
            font-size: 8.3px;
        }

        .exam-table thead th {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .exam-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #fbfdff;
        }

        .exam-table td.index,
        .exam-table td.qty {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .empty-row td {
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--muted);
            padding: 8px;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 7px;
            padding: 6px 7px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: #fcfcfd;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .signatures {
            margin-top: 12px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            border-spacing: 8px 0;
        }

        .signature-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 33.33%;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }

        .signature-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            padding-top: 4px;
            font-size: 7.5px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .bottom-meta {
            margin-top: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 7px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .nowrap {
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% set rdv = consultation.rendezVous|default(null) %}
    {% set patient = rdv ? rdv.patient|default(null) : null %}

    <div class="page">
        <div class="document">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="header-top">
                    <div class="header-left">
                        {% if logo_path is defined and logo_path %}
                            <img src="{{ logo_path }}" alt="Logo" class="logo">
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>

                    <div class="header-center">
                        <div class="clinic-name">Clinique Neurologique Nassarawa</div>
                        <div class="clinic-meta">
                            NIF : 120402/R<br>
                            RCCM : NE-NIM-01-2024-B12-00145<br>
                            Adresse : Yantala Haut, Avenue du Daoura YN 187, Niamey<br>
                            Tél : 20 75 51 02 / 82 09 61 12<br>
                            BP : 2120 Niamey<br>
                            Email : nassrawaclinique@gmail.com
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-title">Bon d'examen laboratoire</div>
                        <div class="doc-subtitle">
                            Prescription et orientation vers le laboratoire
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="header-right">
                        {% if qr_data is defined and qr_data %}
                            <img src="{{ qr_data }}" alt="QR Code" class="qr">
                        {% endif %}

                        <div class="ref-box">
                            <div class="label">Référence</div>
                            <div class="value">{{ code_qr|default('CONS-' ~ consultation.id) }}</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="ref-box">
                            <div class="label">Date d’édition</div>
                            <div class="value">
                                {{ consultation.createdAt ? consultation.createdAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') : '-' }}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="badge-destination">Destination : Laboratoire</div>

                <div class="section-grid">
                    <div class="section-col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">Informations patient</div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <table class="info-table">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Nom complet</td>
                                        <td class="value">
                                            {% if patient %}
                                                {{ patient.nomComplet|default((patient.nom|default('') ~ ' ' ~ patient.prenom|default(''))|trim) }}
                                            {% else %}
                                                -
                                            {% endif %}
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Rendez-vous</td>
                                        <td class="value">{{ rdv ? ('#' ~ rdv.id) : '-' }}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Consultation</td>
                                        <td class="value">#{{ consultation.id }}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Date</td>
                                        <td class="value">
                                            {{ consultation.createdAt ? consultation.createdAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') : '-' }}
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="section-col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">Informations médicales</div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <table class="info-table">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Médecin</td>
                                        <td class="value">
                                            {{ consultation.medecin.nomComplet|default((consultation.medecin.nom|default('') ~ ' ' ~ consultation.medecin.prenom|default(''))|trim) }}
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Service</td>
                                        <td class="value">Consultation</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Destination</td>
                                        <td class="value">Laboratoire</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="label">Nb examens</td>
                                        <td class="value">{{ examens|length }}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="exam-section-title">Examens prescrits</div>

                <table class="exam-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width: 7%;">#</th>
                            <th style="width: 45%;">Examen</th>
                            <th style="width: 10%;">Qté</th>
                            <th style="width: 38%;">Instructions</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for examen in examens %}
                            <tr>
                                <td class="index">{{ loop.index }}</td>
                                <td><strong>{{ examen.tarifPrestation.libelle }}</strong></td>
                                <td class="qty">{{ examen.quantite }}</td>
                                <td>{{ examen.instructions ?: '-' }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% else %}
                            <tr class="empty-row">
                                <td colspan="4">Aucun examen laboratoire enregistré.</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <div class="footer-note">
                    <strong>Note :</strong>
                    Ce document accompagne le patient au laboratoire. Toute annotation complémentaire peut être ajoutée par le personnel habilité.
                </div>

                <div class="signatures">
                    <div class="signature-box">
                        <div class="signature-title">Médecin prescripteur</div>
                        <div class="signature-line">Nom / signature / cachet</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="signature-box">
                        <div class="signature-title">Patient / Accompagnant</div>
                        <div class="signature-line">Signature</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="signature-box">
                        <div class="signature-title">Réception laboratoire</div>
                        <div class="signature-line">Nom et signature</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bottom-meta">
                    Bon d’examen généré par le système de gestion hospitalière
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>